message.content:
cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.CY, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the design and requirements of a communication system for V2X.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses the capabilities of currently available communication technologies and identifies a gap that needs to be addressed.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the role of future 5G V2X systems in enabling more efficient vehicular transportation.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper discusses the potential impact of 5G V2X on personal mobility and transportation.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper briefly mentions vehicular visible light communications as one of the communication technologies incorporated in the 5G V2X architecture.
